    <summary>Provides additional options for creating a transaction scope.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The <xref:System.Transactions.TransactionScopeOption> enumeration is passed to the various constructors of the <xref:System.Transactions.TransactionScope> class to define the transactional behavior of the scope. For more information on how this enumeration is used, see the "Managing Transaction Flow using TransactionScopeOption" section in [Implementing An Implicit Transaction Using Transaction Scope](~/docs/framework/data/transactions/implementing-an-implicit-transaction-using-transaction-scope.md).  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
